Package: nrlR
Type: Package
Title: Access and Analyze Rugby League Data from Rugby League Project
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Daniel", 
           family = "Tomaro", 
           email = "danieltomaro@icloud.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Daniel Tomaro <danieltomaro@icloud.com>
Description: Provides a set of tools for scraping and analyzing Rugby League data from 
    the Rugby League Project website. Includes functions to fetch player statistics, 
    match results, ladders, venues, and coaching data across multiple leagues 
    including NRL, Super League, NSW Cup, QLD Cup, and others. The package is being 
    actively developed with plans to integrate advanced statistics from additional 
    sources to support deeper performance analysis.
